high_descs: Turn left and walk to the counter to the left of the stove.
Take a green sponge from the counter.
Turn right then left and walk to the stove.
Place the sponge in the pan on the left.
Pick up the pan with the sponge on the stove.
Turn around, walk to the wall, the turn right and walk to the table.
Place the pan on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a pan with a sponge on the table.

high_descs: Turn left, then turn left, then turn right to go to the counter next to the stove.
Pick up the leftmost sponge on the counter
Turn around, then turn left, then turn left again to face the stove.
Place the sponge on the pan on the back left of the stove.
Pick up the pan with the sponge in it.
Turn around, then go straight, then turn right, then turn right again to face the end of the table.
Place the pan at the end of the table, toward the right.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a sponge on it on the table.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the counter next to the stove.
Pick up the green sponge on the counter.
Turn right and go to the stove.
Put the sponge in the pan on the back of the stove.
Pick up the pan on the stove.
Turn around and go to the table.
Put the pan on the table.
anns.task_desc: Move the pan from the stove to the table.
